Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fnFZLanTingYuan-DB-GBK\c&H78614B&\fs12\frz12.97\1a&H4E&\pos(642.667,147.555)}有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fnFZLanTingYuan-DB-GBK\c&H000000&\fs12\frz12.97\1a&H9A&\pos(465.778,256.593)}在找東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fnFZLanTingYuan-DB-GBK\c&H78614B&\fs12\frz12.97\1a&H4E&\pos(661.926,557.63)}市川好像在找什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fnFZLanTingYuan-DB-GBK\c&H000000&\fs12\frz12.97\1a&H81&\pos(539.259,625.778)}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fnFZLanTingYuan-DB-GBK\c&H000000&\fs12\frz12.97\1a&H8A&\pos(557.63,668.445)}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fnFZLanTingYuan-DB-GBK\c&H000000&\fs12\frz12.97\1a&HBB&\pos(671.333,683.334)}點擊輸入文字
